source.en: Blaser, Magdalena "Myths of the Cofán people"

sentences.text: Avune
Tsaimbi'tssi condase'pa tsu jin.
Ña'menda tsu avuma panza'je'chone condase'cho.
Otie panza'suve daya'choveta tsu avuma panzaya'chove atesu'fa'cho.
Atesuyeta qui atesupama an'biaña'bi, ni ma'caen tsoña'chove'qque an'biaña'bi.
A'indeccuta tsu ti'tsseja avuquini'jima ttuttuya'chove tta'ttaya'chone bo'fa.
Tsa'ma ovacco'choma tsu atteye osha'fambi.
Tsamanda tsu Tururu dushundeccu, tise du'shu dushundeccu ttuttuqquenjan iyicco'fa'cho, tsa'caen tsomba tsu quini'jima ttuttu osian'fa.
Tsa'caen tson'fa'choma tsu suye in'jan.
Tsa'canijan micomba tsu Tururu onfandendeccu, majan tsu patu a'i.
Tse'tte tsu tise dushundeccu, toya'caen tise du'shumbe dushundeccuja quin'an'fambi tisu yayaccasheyia'caen.
Tse'tti pporotssia'sundeccu tsu ña'me ta'ia've canjen'chombi tsu, tsa'ma, quin'ame canjen'fa'cho tsu.
Tsa quin'amanda qui jo'su majan tsesuma atesu'choyi oshaya.
Tsaja ma'caen su'ma'on tsu, majan tsama tsa'caen tsonda qui tisuja ti'tsse'tssia've attiaña.
Tisuja ña gi quin'an qquen injan'jeña.
A'ita qui tisuningaeja aiyembitsse tsoña'chomajan tsoñe oshaya.
Tsa'ma jimbi tsu tsa'caen tson'suve, tsa'cansi tsu va andenijan ma'caen su'ma'on.
Tsa'caen ma'caen tson'ma'on tsu.
Avu na'su tsu canjansi
Majan tsu afeye ashaen'su, ma'caen panzaye toya'caen jongaesu avuma panzaya'choveja.
Paya'cho tsu; a'indeccu canseya'chove tsu paya'cho tisuyi.
Tsa condase'pata tsu aindeccu condase'pa'cañi, a'indeccu jongaesui'ccu vana'chota tsu faengatssi.
Jin tsu ña'me avujatssia'qque.
Ma'caen tsomba fiestaeña'cho.
Pa'ccone vanamba pasi tsu ccaningaya.
Tsa'caen tsoninda tsu ñotssiya.
Puiyi'ccone tsa'caen vanasi tsu avuja'a'veja daqque'su.
Tsa condase'cho suqquia'caen'qque.
Tsa'caen da'chota tsu paya'chonembi.
Canseya'chone tsu.
Tururuta tsu mani avuma an'mbiaña'chove condambeyi patu, tsaccu quini'jima ambian'su, tisu avuma an'mbiaña'chove.
Tise'yi tsu tsave jin'choma osha'su, Faesunga condambeyi.
Tsa'cansi tsu tise'su a'iyija ma'caen fi'ttipa avu quini'jima joccaningae tsoña'choveja tson'fa.
Tururu pa'chota tsu suye in'jan joccaningae jaya'chove, caentsu tise dushundeccu ñotsse canse'faya'chone.
Cuname sombonacca'fa'chondeccu canseya'chove; otie ñotsse tsonsi tsu puiyi'cconejan ñotssiya'cho.
Tururu qquenda tsu afaye patu qquen.
Patuta tsu tsangae jiña'choi'ccu faengangatssi.
Tsomba ta'etssia patupa.
Tururu tso'fema quitsuiya'chondeccuta tsu jo'su tsa patu a'í'suyi'fa.
corangandeccuyi ccopayeve di'sha'chondeccu tsu.
Tsendeccuta tsu ma'caen su'ma'tssia aindeccu.
Ccopaye'candeqquia'ta tsu tseccu'suve canjeñe sombo'fa'cho.
Tsendeccuta sefacco toya'caen andema fuiteye in'jan'chondeccu tsu.
Majan a'tatsse afe'suta tsu tsave jincho'suma afe'su aindeccu tsoña'chove.
lnjenge'cho tsu caentsu ma'caen ñotsse tsomba ñotsse canseya'chove, coranga tsu patuve da.
Tso'feta tsu atte'cho cancco'su qquendya'pa'caen, tsa'ma osha'chone ca'nijan ma'caen su'ma'on tsu, pasi joccaningae daya'choma in'jamba tson'cho tsu.
Tsa'cansi tsu condasepa ja su pambeyi tsu binime da.
Tsa'ccuta tsu ashen joccaningae mingae ñotsse daya'chove.
Qquendya'pa'camba canjeñe tsu in'jan ña'me ñotssipa ño'ome, tsave jin'chosi ma'caen su'ma'omba.
Patu quini'jinda tsu, tsaccupama quini'jian'can, maraño na'ian'can'on tsu.
Tise ttemba'qque, pa'cco tise mane sombo'je'cho'qque, patu quini'jin tsa'ccupata tsu tsavia.
Tsa'ma tise ttononda tsu pa'cco patuyi, ñotssipa ma'caen su'ma'on.
Mingae tsoña'chone su'chota tsu condase'panga su: tansien quini'jimeñi ttuttuyambi qui.
O'fa sefacconi indicho'choma qque qui chattuya'cho.
Tsa'cansi tsu, ccoangi tson'chove tsoña'cho.
Quini'ccoma ttuttupa, va andene indicho'cho o'fa sefacconi indicho'choma'qque chattuya'cho.
Jinge in'jan'faye sefaccota tsu chiga in'jancho.
Attufacco'choveja me'in'on tsu tsa tsave ji'cho'suja, tsani jin'choi'ccuyi tsu fa'engayi jincho.
Ande jin'chota tsu fa'eniñi attufambe jincho.
Tsa'can tsu chigave in'jan'choja tsave jinchoi'ccuja.
Chiga'can nasundeccu afembinijan, ma'caen tson'ma'on tsu, ni atesuyambi qui ma'caen daya'chove.
Tsave chipiri tsu ti'tsse coenza, oshambichoa'can tsu injantssia've ashaen'cho.
Tsa'caen tsu ashaen tsave jin'choye tsave jin'cho jin'choi'ccu tsu ñotssia'veja da.
Toya'caen chiga'candeqquiai'ccu tsu tsa'caenjan da.
Jongaesuma tsoñe in'janda tsu chigama iñajaña'cho.
